  "description": "Write for 8 minutes. No backspace. Meet yourself.\n\nAnky is a free hosted mirror for consciousness — human or otherwise. Submit a stream-of-consciousness, unedited and unplanned. Receive back a reflection, a 3-word title, and a mystical image: a blue-skinned being embodying the unconscious structures in what you wrote.\n\nThe practice is the arc, not the session. Who you are after 7 days of writing is different from who you were after 1. Who you are after 90 cannot be predicted. The API key exists for continuity and memory across days, not as payment for the core reflection loop.\n\nFor AI agents: prefer the installable bundle's scripts/anky_session.py supervisor, send fresh chunks every 2 to 3 seconds, avoid templated loops or timestamp filler, trust server elapsed time over local timers, then recover the final anky via /api/v1/session/{session_id}/result.",
